---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <!-- Hero Section - Gradient Background -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-blue-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-block mb-4">
          <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-400 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Knowledge That Compounds</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          AI without persistent memory is a brilliant colleague with amnesia. 
          Every conversation starts from zero.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          From first brain-master.md to 12-Brain network with 14 standards, 
          a book, and incorporated company. <strong class="text-gray-900">14 days.</strong>
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/ktc" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            Learn the Method
          </a>
          <a href="/consulting" class="bg-white text-blue-600 border-2 border-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-50 font-semibold shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            Work With Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section - White Background -->
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">The Problem</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Every AI conversation starts from zero. Context disappears between sessions. 
          Knowledge gets lost. You repeat yourself constantly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          It's like having a brilliant colleague who forgets everything overnight.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section - Light Gray Background -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">The Solution</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Build systems where knowledge persists, compounds, and routes intelligently 
          across specialized AI "Brains."
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          This is Knowledge That Compounds.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section - White with Card -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">About Gaudette AI</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Gaudette AI inc. helps knowledge workers build AI systems that remember.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Founded in January 2026 by Frédéric Gaudette, we specialize in the 
          Knowledge That Compounds (KTC) methodology.
        </p>
        <div class="border-t border-blue-200 pt-6 mt-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900">Our Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We don't sell software. We teach methodology and deploy systems that 
            compound knowledge over time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>